FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772457071
OL,3,CBoos at Leeds v Man City during
OL,4,CRamadan pause 'massively disappointing'
OL,6,FCity won 1-0 with an Antoine Semenyo
OL,7,Fstrike at the end of the first half.
OL,9,FLeeds United have been contacted for a
OL,10,Fcomment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
